{"code": 0, "data": {"allow_search": true, "attention": false, "author_title": null, "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "comments": [{"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67439, "create_time": 1649217996, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "这一波清零还没实现呢。等到清零实现的时候，代价到底会有多大？现在还没人知道呢。洞主是要跳预言家？", "timestamp": 1649217996}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67441, "create_time": 1649218141, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "不言而喻，清零伤害大", "timestamp": 1649218141}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67442, "create_time": 1649218155, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "对 Omicron BA.2 强行搞清零的，除了中国就没有了吧，洞主对比的是什么“外部案例”？", "timestamp": 1649218155}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67443, "create_time": 1649218178, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "#24340", "timestamp": 1649218178}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67444, "create_time": 1649218264, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 可以比较香港和上海，哪个伤害更大", "timestamp": 1649218264}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67447, "create_time": 1649218334, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 香港名义上是清零，实际上受限于政府无作为近似可以认为是共存", "timestamp": 1649218334}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67448, "create_time": 1649218370, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 而且现在名义上也是共存了", "timestamp": 1649218370}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67449, "create_time": 1649218391, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "洞主马上就要被举报了🤫", "timestamp": 1649218391}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67450, "create_time": 1649218394, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 当然是上海大……目前我认为已经是上海更大了，等到清零成功之时（如果清零能成功的话），肯定会更大", "timestamp": 1649218394}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67451, "create_time": 1649218419, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 睁眼说瞎话？", "timestamp": 1649218419}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67452, "create_time": 1649218508, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 短时间内死了8800多人对一个700万人的城市的影响会比封城小吗", "timestamp": 1649218508}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67455, "create_time": 1649218730, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我给你算一下，香港的代价是7000名老人，假设每人少活了10年，那就是少了7万人年的寿命。上海把20000000人每人封了至少4天，那就是少了22万人年的自由。至于自由和寿命我不知道怎么换算，洞主愿意用住1年监狱，换取多活3年吗？", "timestamp": 1649218730}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67456, "create_time": 1649218808, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 还有这么换算的？封控怎么就成住监狱了？", "timestamp": 1649218808}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67458, "create_time": 1649218839, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 应该算人均而不是总数。", "timestamp": 1649218839}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67459, "create_time": 1649218841, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 一部分早已退休的老人，去世的时间被新冠提前了。这对一个城市的影响，显然是无法和封城相比的", "timestamp": 1649218841}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67461, "create_time": 1649218879, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以放开后的代价只有一些老人死亡吗...", "timestamp": 1649218879}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67463, "create_time": 1649218971, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 就算让寿命还有一天的人死一百万也比十四亿人封城两周代价更大", "timestamp": 1649218971}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67464, "create_time": 1649219021, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Carol: 如果连这都有分歧，就是道德观的差别", "timestamp": 1649219021}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67465, "create_time": 1649219149, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 那你说说还有啥？青壮年死亡也有，但低很多很多。清零派还会说的是，很多人请病假会影响工厂开工，很多人怕死不敢出门会影响消费，但我觉得越南已经证明了这并没有那么可怕。", "timestamp": 1649219149}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67466, "create_time": 1649219189, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 好死不如赖活着？确实没错，这就是观念不同吧。", "timestamp": 1649219189}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67469, "create_time": 1649219263, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 不不，生命的代价远高于所谓封城的不自由", "timestamp": 1649219263}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67470, "create_time": 1649219277, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 然而事实是越南企业的开工率依然没有回到疫情前的水平...", "timestamp": 1649219277}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67472, "create_time": 1649219345, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: “生命无价”只是个幻想罢了，现实是残酷的。而且共存并不会死一百万这么多，我估计在十万到几十万。对Omicron BA.2 搞动态清零也不是14亿人封2周，而可能是14亿人每人每年封2个月。", "timestamp": 1649219345}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67473, "create_time": 1649219409, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 张口就来？我敢说90%的人过去一年没有封闭过一天。", "timestamp": 1649219409}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67475, "create_time": 1649219461, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 动态清零又不是要清一万年。现在病毒进化还是很快的但还是不可控的，Omicron BA.2威胁性还是很大，当它真正进化到基本药品就能压制时就可以解封了", "timestamp": 1649219461}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67476, "create_time": 1649219465, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 我来问你个问题，每年中国因为交通事故死亡20万人。按照你的道德观，交通出行的一点便利，是无法与生命的代价相比的。那么，我们是否应该禁止汽车？", "timestamp": 1649219465}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67478, "create_time": 1649219556, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 要分清楚正常死亡和非正常死亡，交通事故对于一个国家来说是正常死亡。", "timestamp": 1649219556}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67479, "create_time": 1649219631, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 你可能犯了刻舟求剑的错误，去年还没有 Omicron BA.2 呢。和 Omicron 相比传染性是渣渣的 Delta 毒株就能让西安封一个月。今年三月份以来，吉林已经封省快一个月了吧，现在我还没有看到清零成功的迹象。", "timestamp": 1649219631}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67482, "create_time": 1649219829, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "清零也死人啊，急病看不了病的，慢性病买不到药的，饿死的", "timestamp": 1649219829}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67483, "create_time": 1649219864, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 深圳离香港那么近，很长一段时间疫情扩散压力是全国最大的，现在却基本实现了清零。", "timestamp": 1649219864}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67484, "create_time": 1649219896, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "[![qjM9iV.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/06/qjM9iV.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/qjM9iV)", "timestamp": 1649219896}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67486, "create_time": 1649219989, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 深圳是断断续续，上一波刚清完下一波又开始，而且在每日新增66例的时候就决定封城7天，代价是很大的。", "timestamp": 1649219989}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67489, "create_time": 1649220021, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 从哪里抄来的概念？新冠和肺癌同等概念吗？交通事故对于个体来说是非正常死亡对于一个国家来说就是正常死亡，新冠是瘟疫不是流感，国家政府有义务行使权力或者强制措施保护人民生命安全", "timestamp": 1649220021}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67490, "create_time": 1649220030, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 深圳的代价大还是香港的代价大？", "timestamp": 1649220030}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67491, "create_time": 1649220046, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 一个护士在防疫措施下因哮喘而病亡，是悲剧。那美国仅仅在2021年6月到9月的德尔塔疫情之中就死了109名医生和护士，这难道不是更大的悲剧?\n\n一个孕妇在防疫措施下流产，是悲剧。按香港的情况估算，我们躺平后会死掉的成百上千的孩子，难道不是更大的悲剧？\n\n一个需要做血液透析°的病人，因为防疫措施得不到透析而病亡，是悲剧。成千上万患有本来不致命的癌症的患者，病情因为医疗资源挤兑而发展到毫无挽回的余地，难道不是更大的悲剧？一百多万人因病死亡，难道不是更大的悲剧？几十、上百万重症患者因为医疗资源不够而死亡，难道不是更大的悲剧？被拔管的、被放在一边等死的老人，难道不是更大的悲剧？", "timestamp": 1649220046}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67492, "create_time": 1649220106, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 我觉得你还需要学习一个。死于交通事故是典型的非正常死亡。", "timestamp": 1649220106}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67493, "create_time": 1649220166, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我就问，中国每年有20万人死于交通事故，这难道不是更大的悲剧？为什么我们不禁止汽车？", "timestamp": 1649220166}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67495, "create_time": 1649220180, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 国家每年死亡率没有因为交通事故出现明显波动，就是正常死亡", "timestamp": 1649220180}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67496, "create_time": 1649220183, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: [![qjM2F0.jpg](https://s1.ax1x.com/2022/04/06/qjM2F0.jpg)](https://imgtu.com/i/qjM2F0)", "timestamp": 1649220183}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67497, "create_time": 1649220266, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 3, "text": "Re Alice: 这是自汽车发明以来的传统或者说文化。而瘟疫防控也是传统", "timestamp": 1649220266}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67498, "create_time": 1649220318, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 奥密克戎只是感染死亡率低，但是考虑到传播性强，感染人数大大增加，总的重症人数死亡人数和前几波疫情并没有低太多，参考韩国、香港。", "timestamp": 1649220318}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67499, "create_time": 1649220594, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: 好吧，你对“正常死亡”的定义和全世界公认的定义不一样，以你的为准~", "timestamp": 1649220594}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67501, "create_time": 1649220713, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 你可以仔细比一比数量再说", "timestamp": 1649220713}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67504, "create_time": 1649220792, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "我看到的是上海现在没人因新冠死，却有因防疫死", "timestamp": 1649220792}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67510, "create_time": 1649220971, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Bob: 注意看题，“不仅要比较防疫造成的次生灾害和新冠现在造成的直接灾害，更需要比较的是防疫造成的次生灾害与共存之后的伤害谁大谁小”，上海没人因新冠而死不正是因为当前防疫措施？像韩国那样一天新增几十万例你还敢保证没有新冠死亡的病例吗。", "timestamp": 1649220971}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67512, "create_time": 1649221077, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我不否认在有些地区Omicron造成的死亡比Delta更多。所以呢？\n确实也有人说Delta是大号流感啊，参考新加坡。", "timestamp": 1649221077}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67515, "create_time": 1649221146, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 2, "text": "Re 洞主: 你知不知道一个月医院治不了其他病意味着什么，这些人怎么办，有没有被记入清零的代价", "timestamp": 1649221146}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67528, "create_time": 1649221664, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 少扯越南了，越南去年q3封城3%的增长，今年放开一季度5%+", "timestamp": 1649221664}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67531, "create_time": 1649221758, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Carol: “新冠和肺癌同等概念吗”都是死人，都是政府能控制的范围内，拼什么不同等？\n还有吸烟和二手烟每年造成百万死亡，也是政府能控制的范围，怎么不禁言拯救个几十万人？", "timestamp": 1649221758}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67532, "create_time": 1649221790, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re Dave: *禁烟", "timestamp": 1649221790}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67534, "create_time": 1649221836, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re Carol: “新冠是瘟疫不是流感”这句可以展开论述一下吗？新冠、流感都是呼吸道传染病，有什么本质上的区别？", "timestamp": 1649221836}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67542, "create_time": 1649221983, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 这张深圳小天的图就更不讲道理了，上海抢不到菜是因为本来可以自由开放的商店被关闭了，同时外地/郊区菜农进不来，是人为造成的供应链和供给崩溃；同理，叫上大批医务人员志愿者搞全民筛查核酸也大量消耗人力，一段时间内封锁医院病人进不来，才导致的现在看不上病的情况。总而言之拿清零期间的乱象类比共存状态毫无道理。", "timestamp": 1649221983}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67543, "create_time": 1649221988, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 流感的R0不超过2，奥密克戎接近10，传染能力完全是两个概念。", "timestamp": 1649221988}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67546, "create_time": 1649222067, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 越南2020年疫情控制的不错，经济增速全球第一；2021年被迫解封结果经济雪崩。2022年数据好恰恰是在去年数据较低的基础上恢复的。", "timestamp": 1649222067}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67551, "create_time": 1649222173, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: “2022年数据好恰恰是在去年数据较低的基础上恢复的”：不正确，越南封城是2021q3开始的，q1没有明显的低基数效应", "timestamp": 1649222173}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67552, "create_time": 1649222184, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 共存的时候为什么有供应链危机？政府按着头不让工人上班？", "timestamp": 1649222184}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67559, "create_time": 1649222333, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 我什么时候说过共存一定会有供应链危机？我说的是封城时期的供应链危机好吧", "timestamp": 1649222333}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67561, "create_time": 1649222409, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 供应链危机这个词这几年在新闻界几乎专指的是欧美国家因为疫情导致的供应链危机。", "timestamp": 1649222409}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67564, "create_time": 1649222553, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 那是最早的原始毒株和delta时期的事情啊，现在欧美食品涨价通胀确实存在，但是比封城下部分小区没吃没喝，大部分小区缺食少吃还是要好点的。\n我并没有指望疫情下的经济能恢复到2020以前，但是本来应该可以比清零做得更体面", "timestamp": 1649222553}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67565, "create_time": 1649222651, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 所以你敢保证病毒变异一定是越来越弱呢？为什么Delta变异就是比Alpha还要强呢？", "timestamp": 1649222651}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67569, "create_time": 1649222756, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 确实。但R0衡量的是不采取任何防控措施时的传染性。新冠和流感在这一点上是天壤之别。\n>\n中国每年只有2%的人打流感疫苗，有0%的人会为了预防流感佩戴口罩。\n>\n新冠就很不一样了，我国新冠疫苗的全程接种率已经达到88%，而且100%的人会佩戴口罩。", "timestamp": 1649222756}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67570, "create_time": 1649222880, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: 确实 病毒有一定概率升级成灭世病毒传染力严重性致死率统统max，所以因此就隔三岔五封城？", "timestamp": 1649222880}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67572, "create_time": 1649222925, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 韩国和香港的例子证明了，奥密克戎要么清零要么大爆发，不存在中间状态。", "timestamp": 1649222925}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67573, "create_time": 1649222959, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 病毒变异没有方向，但自然选择（进化）是有方向的。冷知识，Delta在希腊字母表上排在Alpha后面，并不意味着Delta是从Alpha变异而来的。\n>\n虽然概率非常小，但我也承认，Omicron致病性也有一定可能变异到更强。那么我的问题是，你敢保证流感病毒不会突然变异到更强吗？为什么不对流感做动态清零呢？", "timestamp": 1649222959}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67575, "create_time": 1649222999, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 保持清零，可以随时放开。一旦放开想要清零就难了。哪种方式可以有更多的战略主动不清楚吗？", "timestamp": 1649222999}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67576, "create_time": 1649223011, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 新加坡的例子证明了：存在。从清零和共存可以实现平稳过渡。", "timestamp": 1649223011}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67577, "create_time": 1649223094, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 新加坡强制接种疫苗，不接种疫苗不让进公众场所，你国能实现？", "timestamp": 1649223094}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67579, "create_time": 1649223112, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 你是否承认中国也总有一天要共存？如果承认，那固执地坚持清零而不为共存做准备，岂不是会越来越被动", "timestamp": 1649223112}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67580, "create_time": 1649223138, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 而且新加坡照样经历了大爆发，医疗资源也是处在紧平衡下才缓缓撑过去。", "timestamp": 1649223138}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67581, "create_time": 1649223170, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 我还真不知道为什么中国实现不了。有能力强制封城，没能力强制疫苗？求指教", "timestamp": 1649223170}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67582, "create_time": 1649223200, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 肯定会有一天，但不是现在。只要病毒还是严重到还是要封城的程度，对外国的损害就不会比对中国的损害低。", "timestamp": 1649223200}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67584, "create_time": 1649223294, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: “保持清零，可以随时放开”：随时？随什么时？你zf两年多了分级诊疗做了吗？ICU病床涨了吗？什么都不做，每次到了共存声音高了时候就拿各种客观条件说还没到时候。我看这种逻辑下是不会放开了", "timestamp": 1649223294}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67593, "create_time": 1649223651, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 分级诊疗有什么做不到的？难道会比武汉疫情时医院大量劝返轻症患者进行居家治疗更难？只是到时候你们不要像武汉疫情时那样因为被医院拒诊写煽情小作文就行了。", "timestamp": 1649223651}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67601, "create_time": 1649223935, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 一个封城都产生这么多乱象，这么大的国家你能达到疫情放开所需要的新加坡那样的精细治理能力吗", "timestamp": 1649223935}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67602, "create_time": 1649223976, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 一个封城都产生这么多乱象，这么大的国家你能达到坚持动态清零所需要的精细治理能力吗", "timestamp": 1649223976}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67604, "create_time": 1649224077, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以你一个人均10000美元出头的国家要和人均60000美元的国家比医疗资源？", "timestamp": 1649224077}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67605, "create_time": 1649224102, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: \"分级诊疗有什么做不到的？\"你是不是缺乏生活经验？你觉得现在居民看病是优先就近跑社区医院还是上知名三甲？", "timestamp": 1649224102}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67606, "create_time": 1649224173, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Dave: 那你不要混淆概念了，你这个分级诊疗和疫情有啥关系？", "timestamp": 1649224173}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67607, "create_time": 1649224173, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 1, "text": "Re 洞主: 所以你一个人均10000美元出头的国家要和人均60000美元的国家比谁的经济经得起封城？", "timestamp": 1649224173}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67608, "create_time": 1649224230, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 0, "text": "Re Alice: 所以你一个劳动密集型制造业为主的国家要和金融业服务业立国的国家比疫情放开？", "timestamp": 1649224230}, {"author_title": "", "blocked": false, "blocked_count": null, "can_del": false, "cid": 67613, "create_time": 1649224519, "is_blocked": false, "is_tmp": false, "name_id": 4, "text": "Re 洞主: “你这个分级诊疗和疫情有啥关系？”：我笑了，你连分级诊疗和疫情什么关系都搞不懂？\n为什么担心放开以后医疗挤兑？因为长期以来中国人习惯于有个小毛小病就跑去大医院，闲置大量社区医疗资源不用造成局部医疗崩溃局部医疗资源过剩，如果做好分级诊疗就能极大缓解挤兑，然而zf